Description: The minimal-ui-next is a copy of the minimal-ui we should keep the same features and functionality but a Next.js frontend

When necessary use the following commands to run the minimal-ui-next project:
```bash
cd packages/minimal-ui-next && ./start-services.sh
```
or
```bash
cd packages/minimal-ui-next && yarn start:all
```

You will assume that the environment setup .env.local has all required variables present. 

Use async function when using supabase.

Data fetching should always occurs server-side.

